Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nguyen",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Upload ảnh (thay TOKEN bằng accessToken từ bước 1)
POST http://localhost:5255/api/images/upload
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..XapmKmFla8GiGcvP1TA-Hf46NESRlpS81Aw1gguXF2s
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< C:\Users\Hai Nguyen\Desktop\test.jpg
--boundary--

